OL,3,CNewcastle United co-owner challenges
OL,4,C#36m bankruptcy petition in court
OL,6,FNewcastle United co-owner Amanda
OL,7,FStaveley has asked the High Court to
OL,8,Fblock a bankruptcy petition against
OL,9,Fher.
OL,11,FMs Staveley, who headed the Saudi-
OL,12,Fbacked consortium that took over the
OL,13,Ffootball club in 2021, made a bid to
OL,14,Fthrow out the petition against her
OL,15,Falleging she owes a shipping tycoon
OL,16,Fmore than #36 million, the High Court
OL,17,Fhas heard.
