OL,4,C#36m bankruptcy petition in court
OL,6,FShe asked the Insolvency and Companies
OL,7,FCourt to set aside a demand served by
OL,8,FGreek businessman Victor Restis last
OL,9,FMay.
OL,11,FThe claimed figure comprises #3.4
OL,12,Fmillion in principal, #2.1 million in
OL,13,F"legal costs and expenses" and #31.3
OL,14,Fmillion in interest, totalling #36.8
OL,15,Fmillion, according to Ms Staveley's
OL,16,Flawyers.
