OL,6,FThe specialist court heard it is
OL,7,F"common ground" that Mr Restis agreed
OL,8,Fin 2008 to arrange a #10 million
OL,9,Finvestment in Ms Staveley's business
OL,10,Fventures, but that there was "some
OL,11,Fambiguity" about whether this was a
OL,12,Floan or some other form of investment.
OL,14,FIn May 2016, the parties entered an
OL,15,Fagreement.
