OL,6,FMs Agnello, also said that there is
OL,7,F"no evidence" that Mr Restis or Mr
OL,8,FNeocleous knew the debtor had
OL,9,FHuntington's, or understood how that
OL,10,F"affected her in negotiations for the
OL,11,Frepayment of an outstanding loan."
OL,13,FShe said an agreement signed on 7
OL,14,FJanuary 2021 "supersedes all previous
OL,15,Fagreements" and that under it, Ms
OL,16,FStaveley is liable.
