OL,6,FMr Loveday asked the court to set
OL,7,Faside the demand for over #36 million
OL,8,Fbecause Ms Staveley has "substantial
OL,9,Fground for denying liability". He
OL,10,Fclaimed that the 2016 agreement
OL,11,Fdecided Ms Staveley is not personally
OL,12,Fliable and provided for her company
OL,13,FPCP Capital Partners to pay.
OL,15,FMr Loveday called the interest claims
OL,16,Fand claimed legal costs against Ms
OL,17,FStaveley "stratospheric".
OL,19,FThe hearing is due to continue on 19
OL,20,FMarch.
